def solution():
  import numpy as np

  # Define the numbers list
  numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]

  # Calculate the mean (average)
  mean = np.mean(numbers)

  # Calculate the standard deviation
  std_dev = np.std(numbers)

  # Return the result as a list
  return [mean, std_dev]
print(solution())
